<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to KhumaloCraft</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

            .btn:hover {
                background-color: #555;
            }

        .about {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

            .about h2 {
                font-size: 36px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                color: #333;
            }

            .about p {
                font-size: 18px;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #555;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Welcome to KhumaloCraft</h1>
            <p>Your destination for exquisite African art, crafts, and culture</p>
         </div>
    </header>

    <div>

        <img src="/lib/bootstrap/AfricanLandScape.jpg" width="1160" style="margin-left: auto; margin-top: 100px" title="We sell Bracelets" />


    </div>

    <div id="about" class="container">
        <div class="about">
            <h2>About KhumaloCraft</h2>
            <p>KhumaloCraft is a premier online marketplace showcasing the finest handcrafted African goods. From pottery and leatherworks to textiles and jewelry, we curate unique pieces that celebrate the rich cultural heritage of Africa.</p>
            <p>Our mission is to empower African artisans by providing them with a platform to reach a global audience and preserve traditional craftsmanship for future generations.</p>
            <br></br>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
